description: Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home in South Boston’s desirable City Point! Spanning 2,300 square feet, this spacious residence is designed for effortless living and entertaining, with an open-concept living and kitchen area featuring a private deck, exclusive roof rights, gas fireplace, high ceilings, and oversized windows that flood the space with natural light. The sleek kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and a large island, perfect for gathering. Two of the generously sized bedrooms include walk-in closets and ensuite bathrooms, offering a private retreat within the home. An additional full bath and two more bedrooms provide flexibility for family, guests or office. The home also features brand new furnace + HW tank, two garage parking spaces (tandem), in-unit laundry, and ample storage. Located just moments from Castle Island, M Street Beach, this exceptional home is an exceptional find.
